name: I Only Know How to Bully Noobs
summary: That night, in prison, when a prisoner spoke rudely, Chen Ming beat him up — and suddenly, a door to a new world opened before him.【You’ve defeated an LV0 enemy. Gained 1 EXP.】From then on, a martial artist with zero honor and a passion for farming weaklings rose to prominence.An offbeat stat-boosting cultivation story, where power comes not from glory... but from relentless noob-stomping.
author: Marctempest
